{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"synchronized."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This file has to be set together with ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/SceneRecallUnacknowledged\/delay","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLa